title: Drawing, "Palmettes de Couronnement des orchestres", 1833
medium:
Watercolor, pen and black/brown ink, graphite
Support: off-white paper mounted on off-white laid paper
inscribed: Inscribed by a later hand in graphite at center: Palmettes de Couronnement des orchestres/du Grand carre aux Champs-Elysees; for mount inscriptions, see inscription field for 1991-17-2.
description: Two different designs of red palmettes with black accents running across the page, one row facing up and the other pointing down.  Written in graphite, between the two rows of the designs, is "Palmettes de couronnement des orchestres du grand carre, aux Champs-elysees"

tombstone.epitaph:
Drawing, "Palmettes de Couronnement des orchestres", 1833. Watercolor, pen and black/brown ink, graphite
Support: off-white paper mounted on off-white laid paper. 
1991-17-3
